lead_paragraph: Barcelona remain the best team in the world on their day despite unconvincing displays this season, coach Luis Enrique said on Friday ahead of their clash with La Liga leaders and arch-rivals Real Madrid.

headline.print_headline: No Team Is Better Than Barca, Says Luis Enrique Ahead of Clasico
